      "content": "i tried the breathing stuff and it didnt really do much. its still like a stabbing pain when i inhale. i'm kinda worried though, what if it's more serious than just stress? like could the long flight have caused something else? i'm really scared to go to a clinic in a foreign country if i dont have to, it's so expensive and intimidating. is it really that likely to be anything life threatening?",
